<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <title>Virtual Proctoring validated</title>
    <style>
        .virtual-proctoring-container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 80%;
            height: 80%;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .logo-circle {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #0066cc;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        .company-tagline {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .update-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .update-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .checkmark-circle {
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            /* background-color: #8aa74a; */
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 6px;
        }

        .update-title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .greeting {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .update-message {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .highlighted-box {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .no-action-message {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .thanks-message {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .support-info {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .support-link {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .address-line {
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .policy-links {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .policy-link {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .policy-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .automated-message {
            color: #777;
        }


        .automated-message {
            margin: 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .status-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid green;
            position: relative;
            margin-right: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .tick-mark {
           
           color:  green;
           padding: 0px 0px 0px 3px;
          
        }
        /* .tick-span {
              margin: 2px auto;
        } */
    </style>
</head>
<body class="virtual-proctoring-container">
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo-section">
                    <img src="https://proctoring-client-uploads-west.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/assets/bis-logo.png" alt="BIS Logo" class="logo">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Virtual Proctoring Update Section -->
        <div class="update-section">
            <div class="update-header">
                <div class="checkmark-circle"> 
                    <!-- <span>
                        ✅
                    </span> -->
                    <img src="https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NaCfAJtzjP-oa45zd7M1j5FwbA5QBphzgF9284rBdhyxr1oq8H81MYf-v0m1xHk1N536PIRWDkTI4HVLQwTfViXcORVmWWKKKjcVG6LU0aitT99lOjXph1ovuRV8bE=s0-d-e1-ft#https://staging.bissafety.app/images/EmailNotif_Icon_Completion55x55.png" width="30" class="CToWUd" data-bit="iit">
                </div>
                <h1 class="update-title">
                    Virtual Proctoring validated
                </h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="main-content">
            <p class="update-message">
                Congratulations, {{participant_name}}!
            </p>
            <p class="update-message">
                Your virtual proctoring session was successfully validated and no rule violations were found.
            </p>
            <p class="update-message">
                You should receive a separate email with your online course result. If you passes the course
                successfully, your course certificate will display a virtual proctoring verification stamp.
            </p>
           <div class="support-info">
              <p>
                  If you do not believe these violations are valid or if you have any questions, please 
                  contact the Support Team by phoning 1-866-416-1660 or emailing 
                  <a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}" class="support-link">{{supportMail}}</a>.
              </p>
              
              <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                  Thanks kindly!
              </p>
            </div>
        </div>

<!-- Footer -->
<div class="email-footer">

    <p class="support-info">
        If you have any questions or believe you received this email in error, please contact our Support Team 
        by phone at 1-866-416-1660 or by email at
        <a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}" class="support-link">
            {{supportMail}}
        </a>.
    </p>

    <!-- Address + Policies (line before last sentence) -->
    <p class="address-line">
        BIS Safety Software | 261 Seneca Road, Sherwood Park AB T8A 4G6, Canada
    </p>

    <p class="policy-links">
        <a href="{{termsUrl}}" class="policy-link" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions</a> |
        <a href="{{privacyUrl}}" class="policy-link" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>
    </p>

    <!-- Last sentence -->
    <p class="automated-message">
        This is an automated email message. Please do not reply to this email address.
    </p>

</div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
